      • processRawBlock

        public abstract void processRawBlock(Channel c,
                   java.lang.StringBuilder seedname,
                   long time,
                   double rate,
                   int nsamp,
                   int[] data)
        This processes a Raw block of data, do not use this with EdgeOutputers which only deal with MiniSeed like the RingFile, but it is supported for things like RingServerSeedLink which can send Raw data to a QueryMom DataLinkToQueryMom port
        Parameters:
        c - The channel record for this channel
        seedname - NNSSSSSCCCLL form
        time - The time since the 1970 epoch in millis
        rate - The digitizing rate for the packet
        nsamp - The number of samples in the data array
        data - Ints with raw data
